FBIS3-12437 "drnes040_l_94023" FBIS-NES-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Mar 1994 ISRAEL Minister To Demand U.S. Desist From Warning Tourists TA0103111994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1100 GMT 1 Mar 94 TA0103111994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] Tourism Minister 'Uzi Bar'am says he will demand of the U.S. Embassy in Israel that it stop warning U.S. tourists to avoid visits to Nazareth and other cities within the Green Line because of the security situation. Our correspondent in the north Yo'av Aviv reports that according to Bar'am, tours to Nazareth pose no danger whatsoever.
